config FS_FAT
    bool "FAT File System"
    depends on (NAND_ENABLE || NOR_ENABLE || SD0_ENABLE || SD1_ENABLE || USB0_ENABLE || USBH_CD_MST || RAMDISK_ENABLE)
    default n
    help
        This need to be enabled to mount internal or external storage as FAT disk.
        The disk will be mounted as A: B: C: ... by the mounting order.
        The first disk is A:. The mounting order is:

        1. NAND
        2. NOR
        3. Internal SD0
        4. Internal SD1
        5. RAM disk
        6. SD0
        7. SD1
        8. xD
        9. USB
    help_cht
        啟用FAT檔案系統的功能。當需要將內部或外部儲存區掛入成FAT磁碟機時須要打開這項功能。
        磁碟機會依照它掛入的順序被掛入成 A: B: C: ... 。第一個掛入的磁碟機會是 A:。掛入順序是：

        1. NAND
        2. NOR
        3. Internal SD0
        4. Internal SD1
        5. RAM disk
        6. SD0
        7. SD1
        8. xD
        9. USB
    help_chs
        启用FAT文件系统的功能。当需要将内部或外部储存区挂入成FAT磁盘驱动器时须要打开这项功能。
        磁盘驱动器会依照它挂入的顺序被挂入成 A: B: C: ... 。第一个挂入的磁盘驱动器会是 A:。挂入顺序是：

        1. NAND
        2. NOR
        3. Internal SD0
        4. Internal SD1
        5. RAM disk
        6. SD0
        7. SD1
        8. xD
        9. USB

config BUILD_FILEX
    bool "Using FileX"
    depends on ((NOR_ENABLE || SD0_ENABLE || SD1_ENABLE || USB0_ENABLE ) && FS_FAT)
    default n
    help
        Using FileX instead of FAT library, the minimum file system requirement is 320KB. 
        The fault tolerant function supports the following devices:

        1. NOR with LevelX integration
        2. SD/eMMC
        3. USB

        The non-fault tolerant version supports the following devices:

        1. Pure NOR

    help_cht
        使用FileX取代FAT library，檔案系統最小需求為320KB，fault tolerant功能支援以下device:

        1. NOR整合LevelX
        2. SD/eMMC
        3. USB

        無fault tolerant版本支援以下device:
        
        1. 純NOR

    help_chs
        使用FileX取代FAT library，档案系统最小需求为320KB，fault tolerant功能支持以下device:

        1. NOR整合LevelX
        2. SD/eMMC
        3. USB
        
        无fault tolerant版本支持以下device:
        
        1. 纯NOR

config BUILD_LEVELX
    bool "Using LevelX"
    depends on (NOR_ENABLE && BUILD_FILEX)
    default n
    help
        Enable LevelX. Provides flash memory wear leveling function and needs to be integrated with FileX.
        The minimum file system requirement is 384KB. Currently only NOR is supported. 
        Enabling the NOR_PARTITIONn_READONLY partition will disable LevelX and make it read-only to speed up reading.

    help_cht
        啟用LevelX。提供快閃記憶體磨損均衡功能，需與FileX整合使用，最低檔案系統需求為 384KB。
        目前僅支援NOR，啟用NOR_PARTITIONn_READONLY分區將會禁用LevelX並僅供唯讀以加快讀取速度。

    help_chs
        启用LevelX。提供闪存磨损均衡功能，需与FileX整合使用，最低文件系统需求为 384KB。
        目前仅支持NOR，启用NOR_PARTITIONn_READONLY分区将会禁用LevelX并仅供只读以加快读取速度。

config SD0_HOST_CACHE_SIZE
    string "SD/eMMC0 host cache size"
    depends on (FS_FAT && SD0_CARD)
    default "0x800000"
    help
        SD/eMMC0 driver layer cache size, must align on 64k. 0 will disable write function.

        64k:    0x10000
        128k:   0x20000
        256k:   0x40000
        512k:   0x80000
        1M:     0x100000
    help_cht
