    help_cht
        啟用Yaffs除錯訊息
    help_chs
        启用Yaffs除错讯息 

config YAFFS2_WRITE_CHECK_LEVEL
    string "YAFFS2 write check level"
    depends on FS_YAFFS2
    default "2"
    help
        The Yaffs write check level. Could confirm write data errors caused by NAND disturb.
        The higher the level, the more the effectiveness will be reduced.
        0: Disable write check function.
        1: Check only after writing.
        2: Check both before and after writing. 
    help_cht
        Yaffs寫入檢查等級。可以確認由於NAND干擾導致的寫入資料錯誤。
        等級越高將降低越多的效能。
        0: 完全禁用寫入確認功能。
        1: 僅在寫入後檢查。
        2: 在寫入前後都進行檢查。
    help_chs
        0: 完全禁用写入确认功能。
        1: 仅在写入后检查。
        2: 在写入前后都进行检查。

config YAFFS2_LAZY_GC
    bool "YAFFS2 lazy garbage collection"
    depends on FS_YAFFS2
    default y
    help
        The Yaffs will adopt a lazy garbage collection strategy, deferring space reclamation until it becomes necessary.
        Instead of immediately freeing space, garbage collection and block erasure will only be performed when a write operation requires it.
    help_cht
        Yaffs 將改採用惰性垃圾回收策略，延後空間回收的時機。系統不會立即釋放空間，而是僅在寫入操作需要時，才執行垃圾回收與區塊抹除。
    help_chs
        Yaffs 将改采用惰性垃圾回收策略，延后空间回收的时机。系统不会立即释放空间，而是仅在写入操作需要时，才执行垃圾回收与块擦除。

config YAFFS2_GENERATE_ROM_FOR_PROGRAMMER
