    depends on FS_YAFFS2
    default n
    help
        Yaffs2 generate splitted ROM file for nand programmer.
    help_cht
        Yaffs2 為 nand 燒錄器生成分段燒錄的 ROM 文件。
    help_chs
        Yaffs2 为 nand 烧录器生成分段烧录的 ROM 文件。
        
config YAFFS2_ESTIMATED_DISK_SIZE
    string "YAFFS2 estimated NAND disk size to be used"
    depends on YAFFS2_GENERATE_ROM_FOR_PROGRAMMER
    default "0x8000000"
    help
        The estimated NAND disk size to be used must be less than or equal to the actual NAND disk size. Commonly used sizes:
        
        128MB: 0x8000000
        256MB: 0x10000000
        512MB: 0x20000000
    help_cht
        NAND 預計會使用到的空間大小，必須小於或等於實際 NAND 的大小。常用的大小值:

        128MB: 0x8000000
        256MB: 0x10000000
        512MB: 0x20000000
    help_chs
        NAND 预计会使用到的空间大小，必须小于或等于实际 NAND 的大小。常用的大小值:

        128MB: 0x8000000
        256MB: 0x10000000
        512MB: 0x20000000    

config YAFFS2_UPGRADE_NAND_PROGRAMMER_FILENAME
    string "The file name for YAFFS2 NAND programmer"
    depends on YAFFS2_GENERATE_ROM_FOR_PROGRAMMER
    default "ITE_NAND.ROM"
    help
        The file name of the NAND file to be programmed.
        ITE generates segmented ROM files, so the file name of each segment will be prefixed with the ROM file location. For example:
        
        ITE_NAND_0x00000000.ROM
        ITE_NAND_0x00300000.ROM
        ITE_NAND_0x01000000.ROM
    help_cht
        NAND 燒錄檔的檔案名稱。
        ITE產生的是分段燒錄的rom檔，所以每一段的檔名會加上ROM檔燒錄位置。例如: 
        
        ITE_NAND_0x00000000.ROM
        ITE_NAND_0x00300000.ROM
        ITE_NAND_0x01000000.ROM
    help_chs    
        NAND 烧录档的档案名称。
        ITE产生的是分段烧录的rom档，所以每一段的档名会加上ROM档烧录位置。例如: 
        
        ITE_NAND_0x00000000.ROM
        ITE_NAND_0x00300000.ROM
        ITE_NAND_0x01000000.ROM
    
