config NOR_PARTITION0_READONLY
    bool "The partition 0 read-only"
    depends on (NOR_ENABLE && NOR_PARTITION0 && BUILD_FILEX && BUILD_LEVELX)
    default n
    help
        Formatting the partition in read-only mode will not perform wear leveling and the reading speed will be faster, 
        but if the power is interrupted during the forced writing process, the partition may be damaged.
    help_cht
        將磁碟分割區設定為唯讀格式，該操作不會進行耗損平衡，讀取速度較快，但若在強制寫入過程中斷電，可能導致磁區損壞。
    help_chs
        将磁盘分区设置为只读格式，此操作不进行损耗均衡，读取速度较快，但若在强制写入过程中断电，可能会损坏磁区。

