config SARADC_VALID_XAIN
    string "SARADC Valid XAIN"
    depends on SARADC_ENABLE
    default "0xff"
    help
        Set valid XAIN. The value must be within the range of 0x0 to 0xff. The bits respectively stand for GPIO Pins from low bit to high bit.

        XAIN_0 only: 0x1 (0b00000001)
        XAIN_0 & XAIN_2: 0x5 (0b00000101)
        XAIN_0 ~ XAIN_7: 0xff (0b11111111)
    help_cht
        設定有效的 XAIN, 該值必須介於 0x0 至 0xff 之間，由低位元到高位元分別代表對應的 GPIO Pin

        XAIN_0 only: 0x1 (0b00000001)
        XAIN_0 & XAIN_2: 0x5 (0b00000101)
        XAIN_0 ~ XAIN_7: 0xff (0b11111111)
    help_chs
        设定有效的 XAIN, 该值必须介于 0x0 至 0xff 之间, 由低位元到高位元分别代表对应的 GPIO Pin

        XAIN_0 only: 0x1 (0b00000001)
        XAIN_0 & XAIN_2: 0x5 (0b00000101)
        XAIN_0 ~ XAIN_7: 0xff (0b11111111)

