config SARADC_CALIBRATION_VOLTAGE
    string "Calibration Voltage"
    depends on SARADC_CALIBRATION_ENABLE && SARADC_CALIBRATION_EXTERNAL
    default "0.55,2.75"
    help
        Set calibration input voltage. The value must be within the range of 0 to 3.3. The sequence respectively stand for calibration XAIN GPIO from low to high.

        XAIN_0 only: 1.1
        XAIN_0 & XAIN_2: 1.1,1.8
        XAIN_0 ~ XAIN_3: 1.1,1.8,2.5,3.2
    help_cht
        設定校準時所參考的輸入電壓, 該值必須介於 0 至 3.3 之間，由低索引到高索引分別代表對應的校準 GPIO Pin

        XAIN_0 only: 1.1
        XAIN_0 & XAIN_2: 1.1,1.8
        XAIN_0 ~ XAIN_3: 1.1,1.8,2.5,3.2
    help_chs
        设定校准时所参考的输入电压, 该值必须介于 0 至 3.3 之间, 由低索引到高索引分别代表对应的校准 GPIO Pin

        XAIN_0 only: 1.1
        XAIN_0 & XAIN_2: 1.1,1.8
        XAIN_0 ~ XAIN_3: 1.1,1.8,2.5,3.2

config SARADC_CALIBRATION_XAIN
    string "Calibration XAIN"
    depends on SARADC_CALIBRATION_ENABLE && SARADC_CALIBRATION_INTERNAL
    default "0xe"
    help
        Set calibration XAIN. The value must be within the range of 0x0 to 0x1f. The bits respectively stand for voltage references 0.0V, 0.825V, 1.8V, 2.475V and 3.3V.

        0.0V only: 0x1 (0b00001)
        0.0V & 1.8V: 0x5 (0b00101)
        0.0V ~ 3.3V: 0x1f (0b11111)
    help_cht
        設定校準 XAIN, 該值必須介於 0x0 至 0x1f 之間，由低位元到高位元分別代表對應的參考電壓 0.0V, 0.825V, 1.8V, 2.475V 及 3.3V

        0.0V only: 0x1 (0b00001)
        0.0V & 1.8V: 0x5 (0b00101)
        0.0V ~ 3.3V: 0x1f (0b11111)
    help_chs
        设定校准 XAIN, 该值必须介于 0x0 至 0x1f 之间, 由低位元到高位元分别代表对应的参考电压 0.0V, 0.825V, 1.8V, 2.475V 及 3.3V

        0.0V only: 0x1 (0b00001)
        0.0V & 1.8V: 0x5 (0b00101)
        0.0V ~ 3.3V: 0x1f (0b11111)

