config NET_PRIO_MULTI_MAC
    string "Priority for 4G/WIFI/ETH"
    depends on (NET_ENABLE && (USB_ECM_EX || USBH_CD_CDCECM_EX || NET_WIFI_ECM_EX || NET_WIFI_ETH_EX))
    default "1, 2, 3" if ((USB_ECM_EX || USBH_CD_CDCECM_EX) && NET_WIFI)
    default "1, 2, 0" if NET_WIFI_ECM_EX
    default "1, 0, 2" if (USB_ECM_EX || USBH_CD_CDCECM_EX)
    default "0, 2, 1" if NET_WIFI_ETH_EX
    help
        Determine the Priority in Multi-MAC case
        If user only set two different MACs, just determine these two MACs' priority.
        <ex 1> If user consider priority as 4G(Prio 2)/WIFI(Prio 3)/ETH(Prio 1), enter 2, 3, 1 in the block.
        <ex 2> If user consider priority as 4G(Prio 1)/WIFI(Closed)/ETH(Prio 2), enter 1, 0, 2 in the block.
    help_cht
        設定多網卡的優先順序，會以優先度高的MAC進行傳輸，發生問題時會切換到下一個網卡。
        如果設定只開啟兩種網卡，沒開啟的網卡請填入0
        <ex 1> 若順序希望4G(順位2)/WIFI(順位3)/ETH(順位1)，請填入 2, 3, 1
        <ex 2> 若順序希望4G(順位1)/WIFI(不開啟)/ETH(順位2)，請填入 1, 0, 2
    help_chs
        设定多网卡的优先顺序，会以优先度高的MAC进行传输，发生问题时会切换到下一个网卡。
        如果设定只开启两种网卡，没开启的网卡请填入0
        <ex 1> 若顺序希望4G(顺位2)/WIFI(顺位3)/ETH(顺位1)，请填入 2, 3, 1
        <ex 2> 若顺序希望4G(顺位1)/WIFI(不开启)/ETH(顺位2)，请填入 1, 0, 2

